| No body size limits | Medium | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No CORS policy | Medium | Add `cors` with explicit origin list |
| Hardcoded port | Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| Health endpoint disclosure | Low | Review if timestamp is needed |

